casebody.data:
Tuesday, November 26, 1996

MOTION DOCKET

96-2554. State v. Miley.

Ross App. No. 95CA2168. This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal. Upon consideration of appellant’s motion for stay of court of appeals’ judgment, IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion for stay of court of appeals’ judgment be, and hereby is, granted, pending final disposition by this court.

Pfeifer, Cook and Stratton, JJ., dissent.
